text:
Something you seek is
not of this world... but
above it!

Defeat the woman of
the air. It is to the
east you must go.

text:
Come in, sit with me!
Warm yourself by the
fire! I know it can get

colder than Ganon's
heart up here, but I've
endured worse. Once,

when I was in the
Forest of Torian... er,
no, it was... it was the

Forest of Canvula! No,
no, it cannot be true,
for Canvula wood is

always hot, and did I
say... I did say it was
cold, right?

Well, then it was the
Forest of Torian!
